room_title: Escape room "The Secret Agent Room" by Xtreme Xcapes in Charlotte

room_description: A double agent has infiltrated your organization, working only for his own nefarious purposes. Your suspicions lead you to a certain someone, but you need proof to support your case against him and reveal to everyone his true plans. Enter his lair, discover his identity and escape.
